KQL Queries



This section contains all Microsoft Sentinel (KQL)-based queries.
Each query includes a brief description, data sources used, and detection logic.



Categories:
detections/ — Analytic rules for detecting malicious activity
threat_hunting/ — Proactive queries to uncover suspicious behavior
dashboards/ — Visualization queries for monitoring and analysis



Each .kql file includes:

MITRE ATT&CK mappings (if applicable)
Query explanation
Example output or filters for tuning
